        <mxCell id="vWLAzzQPcKAVhgcOkRbt-12" value="&lt;h2 style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; margin: 1.8em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: -0.008em; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Ubuntu, system-ui, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; scroll-margin-top: 56px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;273&quot; id=&quot;1.-What-is-metachain-?&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;What is metachain ?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Ubuntu, system-ui, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.005em; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Metachain is a fully managed ledger database that provides a transparent, immutable, and cryptographically verifiable transaction log owned by a central trusted authority. It tracks each and every data change and maintains a complete and verifiable history of changes over time. Metachain is build on top of Amazon Quantum Ledger Database (QLDB) technology and owned by your central trusted authority (Inveniam).&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0.75rem 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.714; letter-spacing: -0.005em; font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Ubuntu, system-ui, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(23, 43, 77);&quot; data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;297&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Event series are stored in Metachain by default with Inveniam Capital Partners solution&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0.75rem 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.714; letter-spacing: -0.005em; font-family: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Ubuntu, system-ui, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(23, 43, 77);&quot; data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;799&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;The main purpose of MetaChain is to perform data audit of all important Deal-related activity, store it in cryptographically verifiable form and provide a possibility to verify audit data immutability any time later.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="20" y="210" width="370" height="330" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
